title: 342. Andy & DJ CTI: $1 Trillion To Iran, Port Of Oakland Shutdown & Dave Chappelle Show Canceled
itunes:title: 342. Andy & DJ CTI: $1 Trillion To Iran, Port Of Oakland Shutdown & Dave Chappelle Show Canceled
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss President Biden's poise to send 1 trillion dollars to Iran over the next six years, the Port of Oakland shut down after truckers continue to protest, and a Minnesota theater canceling Dave Chappelle's show after receiving 125 signatures & Antifa threats.
